    <!-- ABSTRACT -->
    <h2>ABSTRACT</h2>
    <p>The "Attendance Management System" is a web-based application developed to simplify the daily attendance process in our college. Traditional paper-based attendance registers are difficult to maintain and time-consuming. This project aims to computerize the entire process.</p>
    <p>The system has two main users: Teachers and Students. Teachers can login, view their assigned subjects, and mark attendance for students. The system automatically calculates the percentage. Students can login to their dashboard to view their total attendance percentage, subject-wise breakdown, and check if they are eligible for exams (above 75%).</p>
    <p>This project is built using HTML and CSS for the design, PHP for the logic, and MySQL as the database to store student and attendance records. It ensures accuracy and saves a lot of time for both staff and students.</p>

