    <!-- CHAPTER 10 -->
    <h2>CHAPTER 10: RESULTS AND DISCUSSION</h2>
    
    <h3>Results</h3>
    <p>The project was successfully designed and developed.</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Teachers can mark attendance in less than 2 minutes.</li>
        <li>Students can see their live percentage instantly.</li>
        <li>The system accurately calculates eligibility (>75%).</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Discussion</h3>
    <p>During the development, I faced challenges in calculating the percentage for individual subjects. I solved this by using SQL <code>GROUP BY</code> queries. The system serves the purpose well for our department.</p>

